With access to even more advanced materials, you can upgrade your QFT to tier 3 by replacing the §b§3Cosmic Fabric Manipulator§f §rcasings with §b§3§b§3Infinity Infused Manipulator§§§f §rcasings. This new casing requires even more advanced materials still, including the §b§3Superconductor Rare-Earth Composite§f§r, which can only be crafted in a tier 2 QFT.
